  "title": "Junior Application Engineer (Entry-Level/Fresh Graduates Welcome)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Assist in the development, integration, and troubleshooting of automation systems involving sensors, actuators, and motion control components.</li>\n  <li>Work with DC motors, stepper motors, servo motors, encoders, relays, solenoids, and other electromechanical devices.</li>\n  <li>Provide technical support to internal teams and customers, including troubleshooting and system adjustments.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma in Engineering or equivalent</li>\n  <li>Basic understanding of <strong>sensors, actuators, motors, or control systems.</strong></li>\n  <li>Knowledge of <strong>SQL/MySQL</strong> is a plus.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p>\n<p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>\n<p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p>\n<p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p>\n<p>Registration: R1326740</p>",
